text: Linotaeniidae is a family of soil centipedes in the order Geophilomorpha. There are about 6 genera and at least 40 described species in Linotaeniidae. ==Genera== * Agathothus * Araucania * Diplochora * Paraplanes * Scolioplanes * Strigamia ==References== ==Further reading== * * Category:Geophilomorpha
